<item>
            <title>[PIG-1316] TextLoader should use Bzip2TextInputFormat for bzip files so that bzip files can be efficiently processed by splitting the files</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/PIG-1316</link>
                <project id="12310730" key="PIG">Pig</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Currently TextLoader uses TextInputFormat which does not split bzip files - this can be fixed by using Bzip2TextInputformat.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
